HEADWORD: pure
<hw>⟦Eacute⟧`pure"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<fld>(Fine Arts)</fld> <def>A draught or model from which to build;
especially, one of the full size of the work to be done; a detailed
drawing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

